{"tid":323900,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"四眼性感家姐來港打氣！南非張敬軒爆冷奪三級賽","createTime":"2017-07-16T04:29:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-16T10:14:18.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6fb374ebd940dab197ca30daa939379088d313cd","tid":323900,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T04:29:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170625/large/1498395837_3d7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170625%2Flarge%2F1498395837_3d7a.jpg&h=480bb5cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n麥偉利和姐姐及父親<br />\n<br />\n沙田馬場今日（25日）設有兩項盃賽，其中第三場精英碟1800米三級賽雖僅五駒上陣，但卻特別受關注，皆因有明星馬「巴基之星」列陣。<br />\n<br />\n最終「巴基之星」令人意外地大敗收場跑包尾得第五名，頭馬落在貌似張敬軒的20歲南非新人王騎師麥偉利身上，佢騎苗禮德馬房「馬上發財」爆冷掄元，12倍落飛綠燈Win開出，組合獨贏則不受注。<br />\n<br />\n「巴基之星」今場熱到1.2倍，位置更只得1.0倍，起步冇耐已「fing頭fing腦」跌落包尾位置，完全不願展步，雷神一度把牠收停。<br />\n<br />\n不過，當主馬群跑了一段路程後，「巴基之星」卻重新跑起來，可惜已遠遠落後，最終以包尾第五名衝線，當做正常出賽馬，馬迷投注遂一概當輸，其表現可謂傷盡萬千粉絲的心。<br />\n<br />\n誠如網民而言，「巴基之星」今場演出令人莫名其妙，究竟發生甚麼事，只有騎在馬背上的雷神最清楚。<br />\n<br />\n反觀麥偉利夥拍「馬上發財」卻再做冷殺手，個人繼早前以沈集成馬房「永旺年年」爆大冷勝出沙田銀瓶後，今次又贏三級賽，前駒亦繼季初揚威莎莎婦女銀袋後再攻下三級賽。<br />\n<br />\n其原本遠在南非的四眼性感姐姐及阿爸日前來港探班，兩人今午專誠入場為麥偉利打氣，結果後者冇令屋企人失望。<br />\n<br />\n「馬上發財」是團體馬，馬主之一是早前把名下馬悉數拉離苗廐的許章榮，呢匹南非自購馬在港增至六捷，總獎金突破1,000萬元，戰績出色。<br />\n<br />\n第三場二至四名分別為「醒目名駒」、「活力歡騰」及「東方快車」，三重彩派4.062元，四連環、四重彩及位置連贏均不受注。<br />\n<br />\n全場最熱的「巴基之星」敬陪末席，次熱「東方快車」跑尾二，餘下三匹皆10倍以外的冷馬卻包辦三甲，五駒場合開出逾4,000元三重彩，跑馬就是這樣的！<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170625/large/1498372329_ec9c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170625%2Flarge%2F1498372329_ec9c.jpg&h=b5fb2ee5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170625/large/1498372314_6445.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170625%2Flarge%2F1498372314_6445.jpg&h=56245042&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170625/large/1498372259_3d83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170625%2Flarge%2F1498372259_3d83.jpg&h=5947b456&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬上發財<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170625/large/1498372272_46bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170625%2Flarge%2F1498372272_46bc.jpg&h=7960b480&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170625/large/1498371817_4b7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170625%2Flarge%2F1498371817_4b7e.jpg&h=9c1fae4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170625/large/1498372283_ca2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170625%2Flarge%2F1498372283_ca2e.jpg&h=4c12c494&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170625/large/1498372295_a6b6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170625%2Flarge%2F1498372295_a6b6.jpg&h=dba76b9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170625/large/1498372427_15c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170625%2Flarge%2F1498372427_15c0.jpg&h=94a44a2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/racing/20170625/56873859\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fracing%2F20170625%2F56873859&d=LQWQmKbjtdkBJpbj%2B%2FgmgEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=5b8a01d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fracing%2F20170625%2F56873859&h=ab591d09\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/racing/20170625/56873859</a>"},{"pid":"b4d5942a21046136aee0f245913b132a28094400","tid":323900,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T04:30:57.000Z","msg":"家姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0d5ca434526f6db94f2132fdd6ac61193631e93","tid":323900,"uid":605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T04:31:49.000Z","msg":"南非張敬軒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45394df32848ff0e2549d846e6e4796cb4ecebeb","tid":323900,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T10:13:08.000Z","msg":"以為係就黎坐監果個四眼嘅家姐"},{"pid":"5831bf0140577bac7df2490debacab5999889fa8","tid":323900,"uid":41157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T10:14:18.000Z","msg":"今日贏左幾多場？<br />\n入左幾多場位置？"}]}